longBusinessSummary: FansUnite Entertainment Inc. operates as a sports and entertainment company. It focuses on technology related to regulated and lawful online sports betting, casino, and other related products. The company was formerly known as HIC Horizons Investment Capital Ltd. and changed its name to FansUnite Entertainment Inc. in March 2020. FansUnite Entertainment Inc. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
